{"tid":1322031,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"［農村殺雞分享］ 殺雞用剃鬍刀片割喉放血 仲防止亂叫","createTime":"2019-07-15T23:47:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-16T05:41:30.000Z","uid":4959,"like":6,"dislike":40,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4221e9d2a5173e6205e100388cf495a1ef8c5b1d","tid":1322031,"uid":4959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T23:47:25.000Z","msg":"細細過係農村生活，養左d雞，屋企成日都殺黎食<br />\n<br />\n通常都係用刀片係雞既喉嚨界一刀，放血即死，死之前仲要叫唔出聲。唔死都以後唔可以亂叫。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94d8af24276a8f0954d467c3ec8a029c0f84b84f","tid":1322031,"uid":4959,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T23:48:40.000Z","msg":"其他動物唔知岩唔岩用<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"746d6bfe340a232fe725e8cd5001078e9a40be27","tid":1322031,"uid":4959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T23:51:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d65b06e6289e04770035572fceae064033e615b1","tid":1322031,"uid":4959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T00:36:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75765d103f7c4dfa9acf791b67cd3088b8456728","tid":1322031,"uid":16034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T00:3